        >, 2023, Università Ca' Foscari Venezia, Venezia. Oral Presentation in
        the track "Large Language Models: Applications" <a
          class="badge badge-secondary mx-2 ml-0 my-1"
          href="/pdfs/slide_clicit_2023.pdf">Check out the Slides</a
        >
      </span>
    </li>
    <li class="text-accent">
      <span class="text-primary-content">
        <b
          >6th Workshop on Natural Language for Artificial Intelligence (NL4AI
