      </span>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Talks</div>
  </div>
  <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-10 grid gap-2">
    <li class="text-accent">
      <span class="text-primary-content">
        <b>Toronto is the capital of Canada: Detecting and Preventing LLMs from Hallucinating</b>,
        <a href="https://pesaresiseminars.di.unipi.it/">Mauriana Pesaresi Seminar Series</a> at Computer Science Department, February 07 2025, University of Pisa, Pisa; 
        <a
          class="badge badge-secondary mx-2 ml-0 my-1"
          href="/pdfs/slide_pesaresi.pdf"
        >
